data.text:
Tegan and Sara are an indie-pop band of identical twin sisters from Calgary, Alberta, Canada.

Discography[]

Under Feet Like Ours (1999)

This Business of Art (2000)

If It Was You (2002)

So Jealous (2004)

The Con (2007)

Sainthood (2009)

Heartthrob (2013)

Love You To Death (2016)

Hey, I'm Just Like You (2019)

Crybaby (2022)

History[]

In 1999, when they were 18 years old, Tegan and Sara released their first album, "Under Feet Like Ours," and ever since they have been creating and releasing music. They had been playing together since they were 15, with their band originally named "Plunk."
